<section class="cta-section">
  <span class="section-tag"># get started</span>
  <h2>Build your next collection today.</h2>
  <p>
    Noodle is free, open-source, and runs entirely in your terminal. Get up and running in less than 10 seconds.
  </p>
  <div class="cta-links">
    <a href="/docs/getting-started/installation/">[Install Noodle]</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/wilfredinni/noodle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">[Star on GitHub]</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 4.5rem 0 3.5rem;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--border);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--fg);
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .cta-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-links a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-links a:first-child {
    color: var(--color-green);
  }

  .cta-links a:first-child:hover {
    color: var(--fg);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .cta-links a:last-child {
    color: var(--color-purple);
  }

  .cta-links a:last-child:hover {
    color: var(--fg);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-purple);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cta-section {
      padding: 3rem 0;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .cta-links {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
